name: CUBE GO SPEED
description:
How to play: Use WASD to move and get to the end of the level. There are only 3 levels in total ranging in difficulty.

This is the first game I have ever made! It's short and simple but it took me like 3 days to make.
I used Brackeys tutorial (Highly recommend) (oh and all 100% credit goes to him for the game since it is basically a version of his game :>):

(Oh also I am part of Interdream games, so this is why it says "made by Interdream games student". Expect some games from us in the future :>)

(OH YEAH and theres a bug where the game is stuck on credits and quit doesn't work, just resfresh the page :> its also supposed to say "thanks for playing" and not just "playing"!)

Anyways, enjoy the game! Leave a comment if you liked it or have anything to say about it, or if you want to talk to me too!!
